[{"Code":"en","Title":"Zalopay E-Wallet","Slug":"zalopay-e-wallet","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"0ea65c3d-a38c-40be-a208-d546ab91ccec\"><img data-block-id=\"25681a27-1c16-480b-bf59-9fd27e7e10b9\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Zalopay.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"Zalopay.png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"40d09386-139f-4cf1-8307-2c85d716974e\">ZaloPay is a popular digital wallet and payment platform in Vietnam, offering users a seamless way to pay for goods and services, transfer money, and top up mobile accounts. Integrated with Zalo, Vietnam’s leading messaging app, ZaloPay provides a highly convenient and trusted payment solution, leveraging a vast user base to facilitate secure and efficient transactions across the country.</p><p data-block-id=\"30fe14fe-0843-4da2-9363-069c5c5f6f5d\">When checking out with BCA VA, customers receive a virtual account number specific to their transaction. They can complete the payment via mobile banking, internet banking, or ATM. Once the payment is made, you receive an instant confirmation, ensuring a seamless and secure payment experience for both you and your customers.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Channel Co