-block-id=\"1156c9cd-0a3d-4dbf-b7b7-72cb8feaa351\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\">Refund Validity (days)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"2b4d42e9-f193-461c-927a-3833ecfdda8e\">180</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\">Compatible integration</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"78577504-c624-4a48-b699-21c27370eb5d\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"67ec5201-d0a4-4aa7-a54d-b7c50ee0982f\">Payment flow</h2><ul data-block-id=\"87e150ea-d71b-4e40-805e-37f955bc4810\"><li data-block-id=\"677d6510-f8c3-4c13-bcd0-0ac8963188ca\"><p data-block-id=\"5a988e13-54f6-48fd-bee9-08fdcaf02add\"><strong>Redirection</strong><img data-block-id=\"16b6b68e-fcee-4419-96ef-893a876b58ac\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(72).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(72).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ul data-block-id=\"462e5a3a-9f01-4e27-adf9-47ea1b2d06da\"><li data-block-id=\"f900c838-29ff-400f-99d4-dc688e867927\"><p data-block-id=\"39e9bdca-ba9b-4df1-8360-90ba1e6bc862\"></p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"432605e9-eaad-46ab-830c-06ff594c8e86\"></h2></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"0d216fa4-290e-48d2-89d2-112bc39eed13\"></p><p data-block-id=\"847c89d6-cec6-44b8-bf3e-02bd12ac1a00\"></p><p data-block-id=\"90545216-3d15-48fd-a4ec-7ad9d3bad725\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Zalopay E-Wallet","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"E-Wallet Zalopay","Slug":"zalopay-e-wallet","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0ea65c3d-a38c-40be-a208-d546ab91ccec\"><img data-block-id=\"25681a27-1c16-480b-bf59-9fd27e7e10b9\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Zalopay.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"Zalopay.png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"40d09386-139f-4cf1-8307-2c85d716974e\">ZaloPay adalah dompet digital dan platform pembayaran populer di Vietnam, yang menawarkan pengguna cara yang lancar untuk membayar barang dan jasa, mentransfer uang, dan mengisi ulang akun seluler. Terintegrasi dengan Zalo, aplikasi perpesanan terkemuka di Vietnam, ZaloPay menyediakan solusi pembayaran yang sangat nyaman dan tepercaya, memanfaatkan basis pengguna yang luas untuk memfasilitasi transaksi yang aman dan efisien di seluruh negeri.</p><p data-block-id=\"30fe14fe-0843-4da2-9363-069c5c5f6f5d\">Saat melakukan checkout dengan BCA VA, pelanggan menerima nomor virtual account khusus untuk transaksi mereka. Mereka dapat menyelesaikan pembayaran melalui mobile banking, internet banking, atau ATM. Setelah pembayaran dilakukan, Anda menerima konfirmasi instan, memastikan pengalaman pembayaran yang lancar dan aman bagi Anda dan pelanggan Anda.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Kode Channel</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e208492a-0cd7-494b-82b1-f5c30a1efe1b\"><code>ZALOPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Mata Uang</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"5192cdba-27d8-40c6-b83a-e5462d0814af\">VND</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">Jumlah Minimum</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"2371ffee-327c-423d-b15f-f3c9706f7d3d\">1.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"93c4567d-ddd5-461c-8459-70cc0cce1024\">Jumlah Maksimum</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"50def50a-c13d-40ba-b66c-4ecdfd128019\">50,000,000.00</p></td></tr><t